Given (One word spelt correctly):
  Correctly

Execute (Status code is zero):
  AssertEqual spellcheck#StatusCode(), 0

Given (One word spelt incorrectly):
  asdf

Execute (Status code is one):
  AssertEqual spellcheck#StatusCode(), 1

Given (Text with a single spelling mistake):
  2001/01/01-accounts.pdf
  2001/01/01-statement.pdf
  2001/01/01-line-with-spelling-mistake-asdf.pdf
  2001/01/01-other.pdf

Execute (Status code is one):
  AssertEqual spellcheck#StatusCode(), 1
